Specifically, the petitioner is seeking an amendment to 10 CFR 150.31 that will require Agreement States to notify
the NRC of proposed and completed changes to that State's regulations. The petitioner is also seeking an amendment
to 10 CFR part 2 that will require the NRC to publish Agreement State notices of proposed and completed rulemaking in
the 
