<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(D) communications by a corporation or labor organization to the corporation's or labor organization's restricted
class under 11 CFR 114.3 and 114.5.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) For a communication or solicitation paid for by a party committee pursuant to 2 U.S.C. 441a(d), the disclaimer
